      "description": "Same 10 rows as request 6, added one POST /api/v1/field-mappings call at a time instead of the /bulk endpoint. Kept alongside request 6 as the original per-row approach -- use either, not both, against the same {{demoStepPk}} (the bulk endpoint's uq_field_mapping_step_array_target constraint will 409 on target_path collisions if you run both against the same step)."
    },
    {
      "name": "7 - Run End-to-End Transform (transformation-svc)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{transformSvcBaseUrl}}/transform-pipeline",
          "host": [
            "{{transformSvcBaseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "transform-pipeline"
          ]
        },
        "description": "The demo payoff. Calls transformation-svc's real entry point (the same one a CRM/Salesforce caller would hit), resolving {{demoPipelineId}} to its attached step(s) and field_mapping rows, and returns the transformed Oracle Fusion contract body -- including every demo_* field showing its transform_type applied.",
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"pipeline_id\": \"{{demoPipelineId}}\",\n  \"source\": {\n    \"eventType\": \"ContractAward\",\n    \"awardId\": \"SF-AWD-2026-0238\",\n    \"orgId\": 300000019976011,\n    \"contractTypeId\": 300000020150131,\n    \"legalEntityName\": \"AeroVironment, Inc.\",\n    \"contractTypeName\": \"Purchase Order\",\n    \"contractNumber\": \"W58RGZ26F0238_X1\",\n    \"startDate\": \"2026-03-20\",\n    \"currencyCode\": \"USD\",\n    \"invOrgName\": \"IMO-Item Master Organization\",\n    \"invOrganizationId\": 300000020021543,\n    \"contributionPercent\": 1,\n    \"customerPONumber\": \"W58RGZ26F0238\",\n    \"owningOrgName\": \"SUAS\",\n    \"netInvoiceFlag\": true,\n    \"buyOrSell\": \"S\",\n    \"headerAttributes\": {\n      \"sfQuoteNumber\": \"Q-02120\",\n      \"sfOpportunityId\": \"OPP-4057\",\n      \"marketSegment\": \"US Army\",\n      \"originalContractualDate\": \"2026-07-23\",\n      \"masterContractNumber\": \"W58RGZ-26-G-0005\",\n      \"contractType\": \"FFP\",\n      \"contractClass\": \"USG-DOD\",\n      \"letterOfCredit\": \"No\",\n      \"creditOrPerformanceGuarantee\": \"No\",\n      \"customerAcceptanceCriteria\": \"Yes\",\n      \"dpasRating\": \"DO_A1\",\n      \"uidRequired\": \"No\",\n      \"casCompliant\": \"Exempt\",\n      \"cageCode\": \"60107\",\n      \"naicsCode\": \"336411\",\n      \"contractAwardBasis\": \"FAR12\",\n      \"certifiedCostOrPricingData\": \"No\",\n      \"dd254Issued\": \"No\",\n      \"subcontractingPlan\": \"No\",\n      \"convertedContract\": \"N\"\n    },\n    \"parties\": [\n      {\n        \"partyRoleCode\": \"CUSTOMER\",\n        \"role\": \"Customer\",\n        \"partyName\": \"US ARMY CONTRACTING COMMAND\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"lines\": [\n      {\n        \"lineNumber\": \"0001\",\n        \"lineTypeId\": 300000000324971,\n        \"lineTypeName\": \"Item, project\",\n        \"itemName\": \"140000-001\",\n        \"itemDescription\": \"SYSTEM, TOP, M1/2/5 NATO, HD40-LVV+MOD INT, HD40-LVV+RELAY INT, 2AV, VIGILANT SPIRIT, P550\",\n        \"startDate\": \"2026-03-20\",\n        \"endDate\": \"2026-06-24\",\n        \"uomCode\": \"EA\",\n        \"unitOfMeasure\": \"Each\",\n        \"itemQuantity\": 1,\n        \"unitPrice\": 0,\n        \"lineAmount\": 0,\n        \"lineAttributes\": {\n          \"contractLineDueDate\": \"2026-06-24\",\n          \"deliveryDueDate\": \"2026-04-10\",\n          \"glDivision\": \"100\",\n          \"glRevenueAccount\": \"40000\",\n          \"glProductLine\": \"1054\",\n          \"nonProjectRelatedContractLine\": \"No\",\n          \"avalaraTaxCode\": \"|Exempt|\",\n          \"fob\": \"FOB ORIGIN\",\n          \"endCountry\": \"US\",\n          \"freightTerms\": \"NA\",\n          \"shippingInstructions\": \"Notify Maj Townsend one week prior. Army requests we ship-in-place, see language on page 2. WAWF required.\",\n          \"partialShipmentFlag\": \"Yes\",\n          \"customerAcceptanceInspection\": \"WAWF - Origin\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"
        }
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "8 - PAT-02 Sequential POST Chain Demo (create-contract-header then create-contract-lines)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "8.1 - Define Target (reuse or create Oracle Fusion endpoint)",
